property.title: Chinaman's Ocean Front Beach House
property.description: Welcome to our spectacular Ocean Front Beach House. This beautiful escape offers stunning views and is perfectly situated between Kualoa Ranch (Jurassic Park/Lost), the gorgeous Pacific Ocean, and the renowned Chinamans Hat Island. It is the ideal spot for one or two families to come together and rejuvenate on your own private beach, all while enjoying enchanting sunrises.
